ALTIORA LOGO FILES — DROP YOUR IMAGES HERE
===========================================

Place these files in this folder (assets/logo/):

  altiora-primary.png   — white logo for dark backgrounds (used everywhere)
  altiora-black.png     — black logo (reserved for future light-bg use)
  altiora-icon.png      — icon-only version (reserved for favicons)

SIZES USED IN CODE:
  Navbar:      height: 42px
  Auth pages:  height: 56px
  Footer:      height: 28px

All logos scale proportionally (width: auto).
Retina/2x: supply images at 2× pixel dimensions for sharp rendering.

FALLBACK:
  If the image fails to load, the text logo "ALTIORA" (with blue I) 
  is shown automatically via the onerror handler in the HTML.
